{"id":151237,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/lyx-2-0-0发布/","date":"2011-05-10T03:00:48Z","modified":"2011-05-10T03:00:48Z","title":"LyX 2.0.0发布","content":"<p>利用LaTeX排版的文档编辑软件LyX发布了v2.0.0版本。新版本的发布恰逢LyX诞生15周年。 新版的特性包括：高级搜索工具；即时拼写检查；文档对比功能，LyX可以通过比较两个文档，创建新文档以突出两者间的改变；多语言词典；支持XeTeX、LuaTeX和XHTML；改进输出定制；增强大纲功能；等等。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14af1913/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=LyX+2.0.0%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fopensource.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F09%2F0146245%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=LyX+2.0.0%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fopensource.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F09%2F0146245%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091706844/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14af1913/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091706844/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14af1913/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=cFsNgZHqYDk:c0XsR6Sz1CI:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=cFsNgZHqYDk:c0XsR6Sz1CI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\